    ICompositeElement, IElement, IIdentifiableElement, IResourceBlock, ISupportsUndeclaredExtensions
    Enclosing class:
    Specimen

    public static class Specimen.Container
extends BaseIdentifiableElement
implements IResourceBlock
    Block class for child element: Specimen.container (Direct container of specimen (tube/slide, etc))

    Definition: The container holding the specimen. The recursive nature of containers; i.e. blood in tube in tray in rack is not addressed here.
